==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unionism
<hw>Un"ion*ism</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The
sentiment of attachment to a federal union, especially to the federal
union of the United States.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The principles, or the system, of combination among
workmen engaged in the same occupation or trade.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unionist</ent>⟦br⟧
